	



	ALGORITHM OF ARM PLOTTER USING RVIZ

	WHEN INITIALIZING THE ARM3DPLOTTER 
		-- CREATE A EMPTY MARKER ARRAY
		-- CREATE INDIVIDUAL JOINTS, BASE AND OBSTACKLE MARKERS
	 	-- SET JOINT AND THE BASE TO THE INITIAL POSITIONS
		-- SET UP A CALLBACK FOR ANGLE UPDATE 
		



	WHEN THE CALLBACK TRIGGERED,THAT MEANS NEW ANGLES ARE RECEIVED	

		IN FOR LOOP 
			-- GET STARTING POINT OF NTH JOINT FROM PREVIOUS JOINT'S ENDPOINT
			-- LOAD IT INTO EN_POINT ARRAY
			-- UPDATE THE NTH JOINT

		PUBLISH THE MARKER ARRAY


